title: The Supreme Court may leave alone the Voting Rights Act just long enough to keep the GOP from House control in 2026
description: Republicans’ hopes that a Supreme Court redistricting ruling will boost them in 2026 are fading as election deadlines close in.
content: Republicans’ hopes that a Supreme Court redistricting ruling will boost them in 2026 are fading as election deadlines close in.
